## parseModuleWithTypes() function

> This API is provided as an alpha preview for developers and may change based on feedback that we receive. Do not use this API in a production environment.
> 

Parses a TypeScript declaration string with type resolution.

This uses both @<!-- -->typescript-eslint/typescript-estree for AST parsing and TypeScript's type checker for type resolution.

**Signature:**

```typescript
export declare function parseModuleWithTypes(source: string, tsModule: typeof ts, options?: ParseOptions): ModuleAnalysisWithTypes;
```
